Class LCSCollectionDiff<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • istory.AbstractLCSDiff<Collection<E>,E>
      • istory.LCSCollectionDiff<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Diff<Collection<E>>, Serializable

    public class LCSCollectionDiff<E>
extends AbstractLCSDiff<Collection<E>,E>
implements Serializable
    Diff implementation for Collection (and arrays) using LCS algorithm. Element order is kept, if you want to diff without ordering consideration have a look to UnsortedSetDiff.
    Author:
    Cedric Chantepie
    See Also:
    UnsortedSetDiff, Serialized Form
